1
00:00:28,930 --> 00:00:30,230
By now,

2
00:00:30,230 --> 00:00:33,530
Yao'er and Young Master Gu's engagement ceremony should be almost over.

3
00:00:33,530 --> 00:00:35,430
Once we successfully ally with the Imperial Gu Family through marriage,

4
00:00:35,430 --> 00:00:38,430
our Su Family can hope to be promoted to a Saint Clan within a millennium.

5
00:00:38,430 --> 00:00:40,030
I blame our Su Family for being unqualified.

6
00:00:40,030 --> 00:00:41,300
As Yao'er's father,

7
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:44,160
I don't even have the right to attend the ceremony.

8
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,530
Mother.

9
00:00:51,660 --> 00:00:53,430
My Dual Pupils were gouged out.

10
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,960
Brother Lin Fan was also killed by that demon Gu Linyuan.

11
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:58,030
I have nothing left.

12
00:00:58,160 --> 00:00:59,130
Yao'er.

13
00:00:59,130 --> 00:01:00,330
What exactly happened?

14
00:01:00,330 --> 00:01:02,460
Weren't you getting engaged to Young Master Gu?

15
00:01:02,460 --> 00:01:04,060
I don't love Gu Changsheng at all.

16
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:05,430
I want to pursue true love and freedom.

17
00:01:05,430 --> 00:01:06,230
Is that wrong?

18
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:08,700
What right does Gu Linyuan have to gouge out my Dual Pupils?

19
00:01:08,700 --> 00:01:10,500
It's over. How could you be so foolish?

20
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:11,130
When the Imperial Family is enraged,

21
00:01:11,130 --> 00:01:12,190
billions will die.

22
00:01:12,330 --> 00:01:14,360
The Su Family receives the decree.

23
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:22,630
Su Changkong receives the decree.

24
00:01:22,630 --> 00:01:23,630
The Patriarch orders:

25
00:01:23,630 --> 00:01:26,090
The Su Family will be wiped out in three days.

26
00:01:28,100 --> 00:01:29,960
Thank Patriarch Gu for his mercy.

27
00:01:30,030 --> 00:01:31,960
Su Changkong receives the decree.

28
00:01:32,530 --> 00:01:35,860
With the Gu Family's strength to destroy our Su Family,

29
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:37,830
it would just be a snap of the fingers.

30
00:01:37,830 --> 00:01:39,460
Why bother issuing a decree

31
00:01:39,660 --> 00:01:41,789
and leaving a three-day grace period?

32
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:45,900
In three days,

33
00:01:46,030 --> 00:01:48,430
Gu Linyuan will massacre the Su Family.

34
00:01:48,630 --> 00:01:53,330
Even if we want to escape the Eastern Wasteland, it's too late.

35
00:01:54,430 --> 00:01:57,530
Not necessarily. Things might still turn around.

36
00:01:58,430 --> 00:02:01,360
Rumor has it that Gu Linyuan is cruel and ruthless,

37
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:02,630
tyrannical and lustful.

38
00:02:02,630 --> 00:02:03,060
Then,

39
00:02:03,060 --> 00:02:03,960
perhaps,

40
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:05,630
we can.

41
00:02:07,130 --> 00:02:08,060
Mother.

42
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,800
Please persuade Father

43
00:02:11,830 --> 00:02:14,130
to return the Dual Pupils.

44
00:02:14,900 --> 00:02:17,460
Yao'er will definitely change her mind.

45
00:02:20,060 --> 00:02:22,030
The Dual Pupils were born with you.

46
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:23,160
No matter what,

47
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:26,230
your father shouldn't take them for himself.

48
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:28,760
I will go get justice for you.

49
00:02:29,730 --> 00:02:30,730
No need.

50
00:02:35,829 --> 00:02:36,530
Gu Linyuan.

51
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,760
Return Changsheng's Dual Pupils.

52
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:39,930
To unseal from the Divine Source

53
00:02:39,930 --> 00:02:41,730
the biological daughter of the Undying True Phoenix Emperor

54
00:02:41,730 --> 00:02:42,600
and marry me.

55
00:02:42,930 --> 00:02:43,500
Back then,

56
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:45,160
the Changsheng Gu Family, for the sake of interests.

57
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:47,200
But this woman, relying on her status as the Emperor's daughter

58
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,300
and noble bloodline,

59
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:49,930
refused to consummate the marriage.

60
00:02:49,930 --> 00:02:52,460
In the end, they could only take our origin essence blood

61
00:02:52,460 --> 00:02:54,329
and nurture it in the Innate Good Fortune Green Lotus,

62
00:02:54,329 --> 00:02:56,130
giving birth to this sycophant son.

63
00:02:56,130 --> 00:02:57,100
Return them?

64
00:02:58,160 --> 00:03:00,660
I took this back with my own abilities.

65
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:04,200
This trash can't even protect his Dual Pupils.

66
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:06,700
What's the use of keeping him alive?

67
00:03:10,230 --> 00:03:11,200
Gu Linyuan,

68
00:03:11,860 --> 00:03:14,130
Even a vicious tiger doesn't eat its cubs.

69
00:03:14,130 --> 00:03:16,660
How can you be so heartless and cold-blooded?

70
00:03:17,900 --> 00:03:20,030
A loving mother makes a spoiled child.

71
00:03:20,130 --> 00:03:22,300
If it weren't for your excessive spoiling,

72
00:03:22,300 --> 00:03:24,230
how would he have become like this?

73
00:03:24,730 --> 00:03:25,960
No matter what,

74
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:28,160
he is still your son.

75
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:32,630
You must return the Dual Pupils to him today.

76
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,200
Insolent!

77
00:03:37,130 --> 00:03:40,329
Gu Linyuan, although you are the Patriarch of the Gu Family,

78
00:03:40,329 --> 00:03:42,790
I am the biological daughter of the Emperor.

79
00:03:43,130 --> 00:03:43,760
Today...

80
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:45,760
I'll wake you up then.

81
00:03:46,060 --> 00:03:47,630
A Half-step Quasi-Emperor,

82
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:49,560
the Great Emperor's own daughter,

83
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,730
Huang Mingkong.

84
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:53,130
You've been in seclusion for so long

85
00:03:53,130 --> 00:03:56,130
that you don't even know your own husband's realm.

86
00:04:00,260 --> 00:04:01,790
Mid-stage Quasi-Emperor.

87
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:03,430
When did you break through?

88
00:04:03,630 --> 00:04:04,730
If you are disobedient,

89
00:04:04,730 --> 00:04:06,390
you should be taught a lesson.

90
00:04:06,830 --> 00:04:07,460
Madam.

91
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:10,560
Since this son raised with essence blood is ruined,

92
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:12,260
I think it's time for us

93
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:15,520
to cultivate the Dao of Yin and Yang together

94
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:18,200
and reshape a perfect Divine Son Dao Fetus.

95
00:04:19,329 --> 00:04:21,130
Gu Linyuan, how dare you!

96
00:04:29,460 --> 00:04:30,160
Wanqing,

97
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:32,830
our family is facing a life-or-death crisis.

98
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:34,230
I hope you, fairy,

99
00:04:34,860 --> 00:04:36,800
will save the entire Su family.

100
00:04:37,159 --> 00:04:37,800
Do you

101
00:04:38,330 --> 00:04:40,530
really want me to serve that Gu Linyuan?

102
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,930
I know you have an extraordinary background, Madam.

103
00:04:41,930 --> 00:04:44,130
You are a fairy from the Nine Heavens fallen to the mortal realm.

104
00:04:44,130 --> 00:04:45,190
Over ten years ago,

105
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:47,560
you fell from the sky with Yao'er in her swaddling clothes.

106
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,430
I was struck by your heavenly beauty,

107
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:49,830
daring not to profane you in the slightest.

108
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:50,900
I only dared to use the title of Dao Companion

109
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:52,630
to protect you in the Su family.

110
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:57,220
I didn't even dare to touch your hand.

111
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:59,330
I only worshipped you like a deity.

112
00:04:59,460 --> 00:05:01,560
But today,

113
00:05:02,030 --> 00:05:04,230
the Emperor Family Gu is eyeing us covetously.

114
00:05:04,230 --> 00:05:06,600
Our Su family is nothing but ants before them.

115
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:09,930
I truly don't know how to save us.
